trans-unit.source: Specifies whether a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel"></xref> object on a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.StatusBar"></xref> control is owner-drawn or system-drawn.
trans-unit.target: Angir om en <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel"> </xref> objekt på et <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.StatusBar"> </xref> kontrollen er eier tegnet eller tegnes på systemet.

trans-unit.source: Use the members of this enumeration to set the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel.Style%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel> class.
trans-unit.target: Bruk medlemmene i denne opplistingen til å angi verdien for <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel.Style%2A>egenskapen for <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel>klassen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel.Style%2A>

trans-unit.source: The Style property determines the way in which the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel> will be displayed.
<xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel> objects can display simple text or be owner-drawn.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel>objekter kan vise enkle tekst eller være eieren tegnes.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel>

trans-unit.source: Owner-drawn <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel> objects support displaying images or a different font from the rest of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel> objects on a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBar> control, while system-drawn <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel> objects are used to display only text (or text and an icon if an icon is specified in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel.Icon%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel>).
trans-unit.target: Eieren tegnes <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel>objekter støtte vise bilder eller en annen skrifttype fra resten av det <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel>objekter i en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBar>kontroll, mens system-tegnet <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel>objektene brukes til å vise bare tekst (tekst eller et ikon hvis et ikon som er angitt i det <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel.Icon%2A>for det <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel>).</xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel.Icon%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBar> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel>

trans-unit.source: To perform the owner-draw operations on an owner-drawn <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel>, use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBar.DrawItem> event of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBar> control.
trans-unit.target: Utføre eieren-draw-operasjoner på en eier tegnes <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel>, bruk av <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBar.DrawItem>hendelse av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBar>kontroll.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBar> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBar.DrawItem> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel"></xref> is drawn by the owner.
The <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel"></xref> displays text in the standard font.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel"> </xref> viser tekst i standard skrift.
